    "Before pipelining to the second phase, we convert their formats to fit the target PLs via heuristic rules, thereby formulating 𝑡𝑐 𝑡𝑎𝑟 (Step 4).𝑡𝑐 𝑡𝑎𝑟 can be arranged as \"Inputs:\\n${𝑖𝑛𝑝 𝑡𝑎𝑟 }Outputs:\\n${𝑜𝑢𝑡 𝑡𝑎𝑟 }\", where ${𝑖𝑛𝑝 𝑡𝑎𝑟 } and ${𝑜𝑢𝑡 𝑡𝑎𝑟 } are the placeholders of inputs and outputs of a test case in the format of the target PL."
